{"tid":513399,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[暗瘡]","createTime":"2017-12-29T13:01:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-29T14:03:30.000Z","uid":48648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a83b9e2c054340f51805f9f7e03325422feb9f6e","tid":513399,"uid":48648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T13:01:15.000Z","msg":"暗瘡治理<br />\n1、多喝水<br />\n早晨起來空腹喝一杯水，有助將體內毒素排出。<br />\n建議每半小時飲一啖、建立飲水習慣<br />\n2、多攝取維他命C<br />\n維他命C能有助將黑色素還原，也能預防和治療黑斑等症狀，達到美白效果。而維他命C最好由新鮮食物攝取，如<strong>番石榴/芭樂</strong>、番茄、橙、檸檬......等。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.studenthealth.gov.hk/tc_chi/health/health_dn/health_dn_vit.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.studenthealth.gov.hk%2Ftc_chi%2Fhealth%2Fhealth_dn%2Fhealth_dn_vit.html&d=F%2BAJnKwjjw8KxF%2BwFnr1zZUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=891f79ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.studenthealth.gov.hk/tc_chi/health/health_dn/health_dn_vit.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://t17.techbang.com/topics/25320-effective-whitening-whitening-vitamin-c-fruits-food-table?mode=print&amp;page=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft17.techbang.com%2Ftopics%2F25320-effective-whitening-whitening-vitamin-c-fruits-food-table%3Fmode%3Dprint%26page%3D1&d=F%2BAJnKwjjw8KxF%2BwFnr1zZUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=cfb892f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://t17.techbang.com/topics/25320-effective-whitening-whitening-vitamin-c-fruits-food-table?mode=print&amp;page=1</a><br />\n3、有充足睡眠<br />\n建議睡眠時間大約維持八個鐘幾上、訓之前唔好玩手機、平時中午太攰都可幾恰下覺<br />\n4、少吃味精食物<br />\n避免吃含人工添加劑的食物、減少食動物內臟、海鮮、鵝、鴨、牛<br />\n5、多做運動<br />\n建議每日都做大約一小時運動，跑步、行山、健身 <br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68762287a63cc25d187caca5be7c6f896b692b57","tid":513399,"uid":158371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T14:03:30.000Z","msg":"查防曬 日補夜補"}]}